Package: nccs.data.requests
Title: Ad-hoc NCCS Data Requests (Thin Consumer)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Description: Not an R package — this DESCRIPTION exists only to declare the
    read dependencies so renv/pak can install them reproducibly. This repo
    fulfils ad-hoc data requests combining bmf/core/efile data for specific
    geographies, reading canonical S3 artifacts via nccsdata and joining the
    published geography crosswalks. See ADR 0024 / 0025 in nccs-contracts.
Imports:
    nccsdata,
    arrow,
    dplyr
Remotes:
    github::UrbanInstitute/nccsdata
Encoding: UTF-8
